title: Walnut apricot loaf cake
ingredients: ['120g butter', '140g soft brown sugar', '2 eggs, beaten', '1 teaspoon vanilla extract', '3 tablespoons milk', '200g dried apricots, stoned and chopped', '200g chopped walnuts', '225g self raising flour', '1 1/2 teaspoons baking powder', '1/2 teaspoon ground cinnamon']
